Version 2.2
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

* TITAN2 is now more or less tidyverse compliant; it imports the tidyverse
  packages dplyr and ggplot2.
* new function ggplotTaxa() plots taxa using the ggplot2 framework.
  TITAN2 now imports ggplot2.
*

CHANGES

* titan now issues messages with message().
* vignette name changed from glades.TITAN to titan2-intro.

FIXES

*
*




Version 2.1
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Package first posted to CRAN.
